effect_entries.effect: Inflicts regular damage.  Power increases with the target's current Speed compared to the user, given by `1 + 25 * target Speed / user Speed`, capped at 150.
effect_entries.short_effect: Power raises when the user has lower Speed, up to a maximum of 150.
